description: This week you're in for a treat. I'm releasing the first sex tape I did, even before Maskurbate was created. This is what inspired me to create this website. I saw this guy on a dating site and offered him to do a sex tape with me. He refused unless he wore a mask. So I went to the shop and bought my first mask because of him. The rest is history. It's great to look back at what started it all. Enjoy!
title: My first sex tape, Scene #01
